Double Action is a stylish multiplayer game about <strong>diving, flipping, and sliding</strong> your way into an action movie mayhem. Imagine doing a <strong>backflip</strong> off some dude's face, then <strong>diving</strong> through a window, <strong>gold-plated pistols</strong> firing in <strong>slow motion</strong>. There's an <strong>explosion</strong> behind you and somebody's stolen your <strong>briefcase full of money</strong>.

Is that enough action for you? <em>Multiply it by two</em> for Double Action.

